WEBVTT

00:07.191 --> 00:11.131
(Three years later,
Spring, Year 24 of Chengping)

00:19.001 --> 00:20.461
Pirates! Pirates!

00:22.771 --> 00:24.290
Sir, I beg you, sir.

00:24.291 --> 00:26.101
If you rob us, we're done for.

00:33.641 --> 00:34.680
Song Mo!

00:34.681 --> 00:36.111
It's a trap.

01:29.761 --> 01:30.901
Speak.

01:31.481 --> 01:32.751
Where is your base camp?

01:38.121 --> 01:39.250
Song Mo,

01:39.251 --> 01:40.650
you think you'll find the base

01:40.651 --> 01:42.200
since you've caught me?

01:42.201 --> 01:44.701
We, people of Dongyu,
will never surrender!

01:50.281 --> 01:51.421
Is it...

01:52.091 --> 01:53.231
in Nanshan?

01:54.841 --> 01:55.810
Tongzhou?

01:55.811 --> 01:58.671
Jilang, Zhanshui, Coral Island?

01:58.761 --> 02:00.530
Meizhou, Feiyudao,

02:00.531 --> 02:02.621
or is it Boat Island?

02:07.251 --> 02:08.471
It's Boat Island.

02:11.491 --> 02:12.631
Song Mo.

02:12.721 --> 02:13.861
You crook.

02:13.871 --> 02:15.000
You won't get what you're after!

02:15.001 --> 02:16.530
That was brilliant, sir.

02:16.531 --> 02:18.600
We almost starved to death

02:18.601 --> 02:19.880
because of that dirty
grains transport officer.

02:19.881 --> 02:21.400
- Thankfully, you baited them.
- That's enough.

02:21.401 --> 02:22.370
- Lu Ming.
- You lured the pirates here...

02:22.371 --> 02:23.370
- Stop talking.
- And we finally get to eat.

02:23.371 --> 02:24.511
That's enough. On your knees.

02:25.441 --> 02:27.111
Sir, my brother is new.

02:27.251 --> 02:29.680
He didn't know that the officer is
your father, Duke of Ying.

02:29.681 --> 02:30.520
We beg for your forgiveness.

02:30.521 --> 02:32.160
I understand the anger
after starving for so long.

02:32.161 --> 02:33.301
I would be too.

02:33.561 --> 02:34.701
It's nothing.

02:35.051 --> 02:36.191
Just go ahead.

02:39.841 --> 02:41.600
Fortunately, it didn't ruin your plan.

02:41.601 --> 02:42.921
We got rid of five pirate ships.

02:42.931 --> 02:44.071
That's a job well done.

02:44.721 --> 02:46.141
Just five boats is nothing.

02:49.251 --> 02:50.440
Listen up, Ding Army!

02:50.441 --> 02:51.370
Here!

02:51.371 --> 02:53.741
Everyone, dig in.

02:53.881 --> 02:54.770
In 10 minutes,

02:54.771 --> 02:57.161
we will put on the pirates' clothing
and head for Boat Island.

02:57.651 --> 03:00.181
To safeguard Futing's peace,

03:00.211 --> 03:03.600
we will carve our names in history.

03:03.601 --> 03:06.100
Safeguard the country!
Carve our names in history!

03:06.101 --> 03:08.951
Safeguard the country!
Carve our names in history!

04:28.471 --> 04:30.770
=Blossom=

04:30.771 --> 04:32.670
(Adapted from the novel
"Blossom" by Zhi Zhi)

04:32.671 --> 04:35.910
=Episode 3=

04:35.911 --> 04:39.691
(Futing)

04:46.721 --> 04:48.341
Come, quick!

04:48.611 --> 04:51.461
The Ding Army will be victorious!

04:54.241 --> 04:55.431
It's the Ding Army!

04:56.011 --> 04:58.790
The Ding Army has returned!

04:58.791 --> 05:00.480
- Come look!
- The Ding Army has returned!

05:00.481 --> 05:02.541
The Ding Army is back.

05:04.241 --> 05:06.021
The Ding Army is back!

05:15.261 --> 05:16.210
Did you win the battle?

05:16.211 --> 05:17.090
Yes, we did.

05:17.091 --> 05:18.210
We conquered Boat Island.

05:18.211 --> 05:21.100
With peace restored on the seas,
your goods will be worth much more now.

05:21.101 --> 05:21.970
That's great news!

05:21.971 --> 05:23.871
This is so grand.

05:24.361 --> 05:25.360
Get used to it.

05:25.361 --> 05:26.501
This is nothing.

05:26.501 --> 05:27.890
There will be grander receptions
in the future.

05:27.891 --> 05:29.140
The Ding Army is great!

05:29.141 --> 05:30.600
- Ding Army!
- The Ding Army is great!

05:30.601 --> 05:32.071
Thank goodness for the Ding Army.

05:32.531 --> 05:33.390
Lu Zheng,

05:33.391 --> 05:34.480
notify the army division

05:34.481 --> 05:36.331
to escort the captive women
and children back to Dongyu.

05:36.331 --> 05:37.870
If the army dares abuse the children

05:37.871 --> 05:38.890
The Ding Army is great!

05:38.891 --> 05:40.071
or violate the women,

05:40.071 --> 05:41.090
they will be punished by military law.

05:41.091 --> 05:42.231
Yes, sir.

05:44.361 --> 05:45.541
Congratulations, Marshal.

05:45.801 --> 05:47.800
The news of your conquest of Boat Island

05:47.801 --> 05:49.191
has reached the military base.

05:49.651 --> 05:50.951
Duke of Ying has come too.

05:51.571 --> 05:52.711
Father is here?

05:56.531 --> 05:57.671
Jiang Meisun!

05:58.371 --> 05:59.600
The delay in delivering grains

05:59.601 --> 06:01.221
(Song Yichun, Duke of Ying)
was due to attacks from pirates.

06:01.361 --> 06:03.871
What is wrong about eliminating evils
for the people?

06:04.281 --> 06:05.421
Let me go!

06:05.891 --> 06:07.391
- Let me go!
- Sir.

06:07.601 --> 06:09.221
He is after all Duke of Ying,

06:09.651 --> 06:10.901
your brother-in-law.

06:10.921 --> 06:12.221
Listen up.

06:14.211 --> 06:16.781
Song Yichun failed
to carry out his duties.

06:18.211 --> 06:20.311
On top of that,
he's making wild statements.

06:21.161 --> 06:22.311
According to military law,

06:23.161 --> 06:24.701
he is sentenced to 30 whips.

06:25.161 --> 06:26.090
Execute the punishment.

06:26.091 --> 06:26.940
Yes, sir.

06:26.941 --> 06:27.920
You dare do it?

06:27.921 --> 06:30.130
I am a high-ranking decorated duke.

06:30.131 --> 06:32.341
Without the royal decree,
don't anyone dare touch me!

06:36.841 --> 06:37.981
Marshal!

06:51.841 --> 06:52.981
Son!

06:55.891 --> 06:56.730
Sir,

06:56.731 --> 06:58.360
fortunately,
I have fulfilled my mission.

06:58.361 --> 06:59.501
On your feet.

07:00.181 --> 07:01.360
We were running of our food.

07:01.361 --> 07:02.690
Because you used yourself as bait,

07:02.691 --> 07:04.280
we were able to subdue
Dongyu's military power.

07:04.281 --> 07:05.901
Good work! You must be rewarded.

07:06.891 --> 07:08.031
Sir,

07:08.281 --> 07:10.461
the deputy marshal not only
destroyed ten pirate ships,

07:10.601 --> 07:12.530
he also made use of them
to take down Boat Island.

07:12.531 --> 07:14.871
The pirates' last island
has also been eliminated.

07:15.141 --> 07:17.650
The decade-long efforts in border
control and pacifying the seas

07:17.651 --> 07:18.720
have finally succeeded.

07:18.721 --> 07:21.461
Awesome!

07:24.571 --> 07:25.711
Young man.

07:25.771 --> 07:27.661
Your supplies were limited,

07:27.971 --> 07:29.221
and so was your manpower.

07:29.651 --> 07:31.581
Were you trying to get yourself killed?

07:32.841 --> 07:34.541
It's because of the delay
in food delivery,

07:34.721 --> 07:36.901
that's why my son had to risk his life
to save everyone!

07:37.361 --> 07:38.501
Son,

07:38.571 --> 07:40.141
talk some sense into your uncle.

07:40.331 --> 07:41.890
I refuse to waste time arguing with him.

07:41.891 --> 07:43.031
Incredulous!

07:43.531 --> 07:45.160
The army is governed by law.

07:45.161 --> 07:46.591
There is no place for familial bonds.

07:46.841 --> 07:49.280
Failure to prioritize, greedy for merit
for suppressing bandits,

07:49.281 --> 07:50.690
you delayed the operation for ten days!

07:50.691 --> 07:52.210
If Song Mo hadn't stepped up
at the critical moment,

07:52.211 --> 07:53.240
this battle would've been lost.

07:53.241 --> 07:54.570
How dare you say that!

07:54.571 --> 07:55.480
Bring me the whip!

07:55.481 --> 07:56.890
I will execute punishment myself!

07:56.891 --> 07:58.840
- I dare you!
- Watch me!

07:58.841 --> 07:59.981
Sir.

08:00.161 --> 08:02.141
Duke of Ying is guilty
of dereliction of duty.

08:02.691 --> 08:03.970
But to watch on

08:03.971 --> 08:05.581
as my elderly father gets punished

08:05.841 --> 08:07.341
is also a failure on my part.

08:08.091 --> 08:09.271
Thirty whips

08:09.941 --> 08:11.271
is like a death sentence to him.

08:11.451 --> 08:12.901
I did no wrong!

08:14.281 --> 08:15.431
Please, sir.

08:15.921 --> 08:17.781
Considering our victory on Boat Island,

08:18.091 --> 08:20.751
allow me to receive
the punishment in my father's place.

08:21.211 --> 08:22.581
It is not against the law,

08:22.921 --> 08:24.221
and is a show of my loyalty.

08:26.971 --> 08:28.720
Please have mercy, Marshal!

08:28.721 --> 08:30.650
Please have mercy, Marshal!

08:30.651 --> 08:32.581
Please have mercy, Marshal!

08:42.971 --> 08:45.021
A show of loyalty, huh?

08:53.971 --> 08:55.111
Well then...

08:56.411 --> 08:57.871
you get your wish.

08:58.451 --> 09:00.141
I'll increase it by 10 whips.

09:01.931 --> 09:03.071
Will you take it?

09:07.841 --> 09:08.981
Yes.

09:10.481 --> 09:11.621
I'm sorry.

09:20.481 --> 09:21.621
Go!

09:22.121 --> 09:24.541
How did a failure
produce such a distinguished son?

09:25.811 --> 09:27.021
Unbelievable!

09:42.361 --> 09:43.541
Hang in there.

09:48.451 --> 09:49.871
Young man.

09:50.451 --> 09:52.271
How did you ever think
to attack Boat Island

09:52.411 --> 09:54.271
with only a handful of men?

09:54.721 --> 09:56.351
You put yourself in danger,

09:56.591 --> 09:57.871
how reckless.

09:59.521 --> 10:00.661
The Art of War states,

10:02.121 --> 10:03.871
throw them into a desperate
situation and they will survive.

10:03.971 --> 10:05.541
Place them in a position of certain
death and they will then live.

10:06.091 --> 10:07.941
An army that fights with grief
and despair is destined to win.

10:08.451 --> 10:09.631
You taught me this.

10:12.691 --> 10:15.061
Don't you talk about
military strategy with me, boy.

10:15.361 --> 10:17.271
I wasn't there,

10:17.481 --> 10:19.591
but I know very well
what you were thinking.

10:20.091 --> 10:21.360
You attacked Boat Island

10:21.361 --> 10:24.021
because you wanted to make up
for your father's sins.

10:26.811 --> 10:28.471
Now you've seen for yourself.

10:28.641 --> 10:29.781
Was it worth it?

10:30.721 --> 10:32.391
You actually went ahead and beat him?

10:33.291 --> 10:34.431
I told him to.

10:34.771 --> 10:36.111
The military is not child's play.

10:36.601 --> 10:37.751
It was only 40 whips.

10:37.931 --> 10:39.290
I meant it when I said

10:39.291 --> 10:40.991
I'd bear it for my father.

10:41.691 --> 10:42.810
Leave us.

10:42.811 --> 10:43.991
- Yes, sir.
- Yes, sir.

10:47.721 --> 10:48.861
Uncle.

10:49.641 --> 10:51.781
Worth it or not, he is still my father.

10:51.931 --> 10:53.391
My mother and Han

10:53.811 --> 10:55.351
are waiting for him at home.

10:57.451 --> 10:58.711
It's all my fault.

10:58.971 --> 10:59.880
Back then,

10:59.881 --> 11:02.421
I should never have agreed
to let him marry Huisun.

11:03.691 --> 11:04.901
That's not right.

11:05.581 --> 11:07.690
I wouldn't be here if Father and Mother
hadn't gotten married.

11:07.691 --> 11:08.690
Without me,

11:08.691 --> 11:10.471
who would protect the seas
alongside you?

11:10.481 --> 11:11.941
You would've been so bored.

11:12.521 --> 11:13.661
Right now,

11:14.451 --> 11:16.480
I feel like I just had
a cupping session,

11:16.481 --> 11:17.871
I'm rejuvenated.

11:18.761 --> 11:19.840
Is this rejuvenating?

11:19.841 --> 11:20.981
Is it?

11:26.571 --> 11:28.391
Duke of Ying has left.

11:44.791 --> 11:46.771
(Abundance)

12:02.231 --> 12:04.451
(Abundance)

12:10.601 --> 12:12.120
Light a lantern and incense,

12:12.121 --> 12:13.210
(Zhao Zhangru)
I pray for God's blessings.

12:13.211 --> 12:15.421
May the warehouses
be filled with good harvest.

12:15.451 --> 12:16.690
May Ms. Longevity and Ansu

12:16.691 --> 12:18.711
make bucket loads of money.

12:22.001 --> 12:24.000
A farmer's livelihood is dependent
on the weather.

12:24.070 --> 12:25.141
Rain or shine, nobody knows for sure.

12:25.171 --> 12:25.944
(Fair weather cometh)
That's why

12:25.945 --> 12:27.301
(Fair weather cometh)
we have to pray for good weather.

12:27.361 --> 12:29.421
Doing business
is all about our own effort.

12:29.721 --> 12:31.511
Rather than praying to the gods,

12:31.881 --> 12:33.421
isn't it better to reward me instead?

12:35.211 --> 12:36.410
Watch what you say.

12:36.411 --> 12:38.941
Sailing the seas relies
on heavenly will.

12:39.241 --> 12:41.240
Dear God, please don't mind Ms. Longevity.

12:41.241 --> 12:42.480
If you have the time,

12:42.481 --> 12:43.600
please do watch over us.

12:43.601 --> 12:45.301
Bless us with more wealth and fortune.

12:46.641 --> 12:49.421
My guess is that the pirates
will be eliminated by the year end.

12:49.491 --> 12:52.301
The maritime trade will experience
a great boon in spring and summer.

12:52.411 --> 12:54.301
I will get you your wealth and fortune.

12:54.811 --> 12:58.061
You are like the all-knowing
female Zhuge.

12:58.481 --> 13:00.661
But did you see this coming?

13:02.361 --> 13:03.511
Zhangru!

13:04.051 --> 13:04.890
Okay.

13:04.891 --> 13:05.970
I have another intuition.

13:05.971 --> 13:08.541
You won't be getting
a matrilocal husband this year either.

13:09.121 --> 13:11.391
How dare you say that?

13:12.241 --> 13:13.381
Zhangru!

13:26.521 --> 13:27.711
Good news!

13:27.971 --> 13:29.471
I've got great news!

13:31.091 --> 13:32.751
- Su.
- Su.

13:33.331 --> 13:34.871
What are you two doing?

13:37.521 --> 13:38.871
What are you doing?

13:39.761 --> 13:41.181
- Stop it!
- Come here.

13:43.411 --> 13:44.551
Stop it!

13:49.841 --> 13:50.981
Oh no.

13:51.001 --> 13:52.231
What's that?

13:52.361 --> 13:53.501
Money.

13:56.881 --> 13:58.941
I didn't guess they'd be silver notes,

14:00.091 --> 14:01.720
worth 1000 taels each.

14:01.721 --> 14:03.140
And there's a thick stack.

14:03.141 --> 14:04.000
I doubt you'd find anyone

14:04.001 --> 14:05.520
with this many notes
in the whole of Northern Zhili.

14:05.521 --> 14:08.570
The tea leaves, silk and ceramics
that we stockpiled last year

14:08.571 --> 14:09.840
all increased in prices.

14:09.841 --> 14:11.751
It's all thanks to Zhao's tip.

14:12.211 --> 14:13.520
My father said,

14:13.521 --> 14:16.120
the orders from merchant ships
increased by tenfold this month.

14:16.121 --> 14:17.991
The earnings will only get bigger.

14:19.331 --> 14:20.471
Ansu,

14:20.521 --> 14:22.330
go back and tell Mr. and Mrs. Miao

14:22.331 --> 14:24.511
to sell the merchant ships

14:24.521 --> 14:25.961
after the current goods are cleared.

14:25.971 --> 14:27.670
We'll look for another
business opportunity.

14:28.451 --> 14:30.111
Are you serious, Ms. Longevity?

14:30.641 --> 14:31.720
Yeah,

14:31.721 --> 14:33.970
we've managed to get a head start
in Futing.

14:33.971 --> 14:35.541
We're the top sea merchant.

14:35.641 --> 14:36.840
Very soon,

14:36.841 --> 14:38.810
all the waterways will be connected.

14:38.811 --> 14:40.810
Wouldn't we make even more money then?

14:40.811 --> 14:42.901
We're in the 24th year of Chengping.

14:42.901 --> 14:45.351
The Ding Army's mission to pacify
the seas is coming to fruition.

14:45.811 --> 14:47.021
With the pirates eliminated,

14:47.171 --> 14:49.821
maritime trade will be extremely
profitable without any obstacles.

14:49.971 --> 14:52.541
From the local Futing magistrate
to the Ministry of Revenue,

14:52.971 --> 14:54.821
they will surely implement levies.

14:55.331 --> 14:57.541
I reckon this business won't be as easy.

14:57.641 --> 15:00.111
Even if the local officials want a cut,

15:00.171 --> 15:02.170
it's not to the extent
of giving it up entirely, right?

15:02.171 --> 15:04.351
Isn't it too soon to back out?

15:04.601 --> 15:07.290
Or is it because you heard something

15:07.291 --> 15:08.330
from Mr. Chen?

15:08.331 --> 15:09.541
No.

15:09.881 --> 15:12.090
Buy when prices are low,

15:12.091 --> 15:13.450
even if they later rise,
you bought at a low price.

15:13.451 --> 15:15.970
Sell when prices are high, even if they
later drop, you sold at a high price.

15:15.971 --> 15:17.871
Everyone knows this business
is a windfall.

15:17.881 --> 15:19.141
So there's no profit to be made.

15:19.601 --> 15:20.741
Just trust me.

15:21.241 --> 15:22.080
I don't get it,

15:22.081 --> 15:23.351
but I know one thing.

15:23.641 --> 15:25.570
If you become
the richest person in Zhending,

15:25.571 --> 15:26.450
your stepmother

15:26.451 --> 15:28.600
and that wannabe relative,
Marquis of Jining,

15:28.601 --> 15:30.391
would surely be desirous.

15:30.691 --> 15:31.831
Fourth Young Lady.

15:32.331 --> 15:33.901
Nanny Zhou from the capital is here.

15:35.601 --> 15:36.450
See?

15:36.451 --> 15:37.690
Speak of the devil.

15:37.691 --> 15:39.421
Here comes trouble.

15:39.481 --> 15:42.781
I said no to your family's
new year party long ago.

15:43.331 --> 15:44.901
Now, you've come asking again.

15:45.291 --> 15:47.541
I have relatives
from afar visiting today.

15:47.761 --> 15:49.751
So I've no time
to be the gracious elder.

15:50.841 --> 15:53.480
Old Madam, you sure know how to jest.

15:53.481 --> 15:55.781
It's rare for Fifth Master
and Seventh Master to be present.

15:55.931 --> 15:57.480
It will be a grand family reunion.

15:57.481 --> 15:59.541
Isn't it nice for everyone to gather?

16:00.571 --> 16:01.781
I'll be frank.

16:02.171 --> 16:04.991
Seventh Master fell ill a few days ago.

16:05.411 --> 16:07.301
He misses his daughter.

16:08.641 --> 16:10.021
You're using Father as an excuse?

16:10.121 --> 16:12.541
So I'd be the bad daughter
if I didn't go.

16:13.451 --> 16:15.480
Don't say that, Miss.

16:15.481 --> 16:17.240
Madam prepared a full spread of dishes

16:17.241 --> 16:19.941
in anticipating of your arrival.

16:20.481 --> 16:21.790
She cooked?

16:21.791 --> 16:23.090
Are you sure it's edible?

16:23.091 --> 16:24.000
Right.

16:24.001 --> 16:25.781
Who knows what she's up to?

16:25.971 --> 16:28.021
She might have added poison to the dish.

16:28.281 --> 16:29.600
There's no way I'm falling for it.

16:29.601 --> 16:31.511
Come on, it's not like that.

16:32.361 --> 16:33.501
Alright.

16:34.841 --> 16:36.421
You're going, Ms. Longevity?

16:38.481 --> 16:39.621
Grandmother,

16:39.641 --> 16:41.541
at least Father remembered me.

16:42.331 --> 16:43.450
I will go.

16:43.451 --> 16:45.690
We'll go with Zhao then.

16:45.691 --> 16:46.970
I reckon the residence

16:46.971 --> 16:48.781
wouldn't mind feeding
a couple more mouths.

16:50.841 --> 16:51.981
Alright.

16:52.601 --> 16:55.751
It takes only half a day to get
to the capital from Zhending.

16:56.721 --> 16:57.861
Nanny Zhou,

16:58.481 --> 17:00.690
please take good care
of my granddaughters.

17:00.691 --> 17:02.061
Certainly.

17:04.281 --> 17:05.330
How are things today?

17:05.331 --> 17:06.620
Good harvest.

17:06.621 --> 17:07.470
That's great.

17:07.471 --> 17:09.040
Candied hawthorns!

17:09.041 --> 17:09.890
I'll have one.

17:09.891 --> 17:12.371
(Duke of Ying's Residence)

17:40.631 --> 17:42.891
(Song Han, Duke of Ying's Second Son)

17:45.971 --> 17:47.231
Han's mastery of the spear

17:47.241 --> 17:49.021
has improved a lot.

17:49.271 --> 17:52.131
I suppose it took a toll on your mother.

17:52.991 --> 17:54.371
There's no such thing.

17:54.511 --> 17:56.070
I haven't wielded a spear
in a long time.

17:56.071 --> 17:57.030
Nowadays,

17:57.031 --> 17:58.811
it's good for me to keep active.

18:05.551 --> 18:06.510
Mo!

18:06.511 --> 18:07.651
You're back.

18:08.111 --> 18:09.251
Son.

18:09.511 --> 18:10.651
My son.

18:12.271 --> 18:13.411
Mother.

18:15.751 --> 18:17.571
This is a blade I got from the pirates.

18:17.791 --> 18:18.931
I want you to have it.

18:21.191 --> 18:22.331
Thank you, Mo.

18:23.851 --> 18:26.491
I heard you were badly injured
from the battle on Boat Island.

18:26.671 --> 18:27.630
Where are you hurt?

18:27.631 --> 18:28.771
Let me see.

18:28.951 --> 18:30.091
I'm alright.

18:32.071 --> 18:33.491
It must have been a hard journey.

18:33.511 --> 18:35.051
I'm sure you've suffered.

18:35.751 --> 18:38.851
Are you going to boast
about your victory from the get-go?

18:39.551 --> 18:41.491
His uncle took care of his wounds.

18:41.951 --> 18:43.211
There's no need for us.

18:46.231 --> 18:48.070
Could you stop sulking about my brother?

18:48.071 --> 18:49.531
The boys are still here.

18:54.471 --> 18:55.611
Leave him there.

18:57.271 --> 18:58.230
It's been a while

18:58.231 --> 18:59.971
since you've had my cooking, right?

19:00.711 --> 19:01.710
Go and rest up.

19:01.711 --> 19:03.731
I will personally cook today.

19:03.831 --> 19:06.051
Let's have a good family meal later.

19:06.071 --> 19:07.950
Sounds good. I'll help you, Mother.

19:07.951 --> 19:09.091
Okay.

19:17.031 --> 19:18.171
Leave us.

19:29.391 --> 19:31.371
What a move from your uncle.

19:31.391 --> 19:33.531
He sent a military notice urgently.

19:34.031 --> 19:35.750
It stated how I was negligent

19:35.751 --> 19:38.451
and was only spared from whipping
due to my son's meritorious service.

19:39.071 --> 19:42.051
Now, the officials all knew it.

19:42.151 --> 19:43.390
I

19:43.391 --> 19:44.830
have to rely on my good son

19:44.831 --> 19:47.291
to have Jiang Meisun let me go?

19:47.751 --> 19:49.371
This is a military notice
on the victory,

19:49.471 --> 19:50.611
not an impeachment letter.

19:50.991 --> 19:52.070
It's mainly to share

19:52.071 --> 19:53.731
the good news of the victory.

19:54.031 --> 19:56.251
So His Majesty wouldn't focus
on you mistake.

19:56.351 --> 19:58.611
Was I wrong in helping the people
get rid of the bandits?

19:59.231 --> 20:00.910
If you hadn't asked to be punished,

20:00.911 --> 20:03.471
I would've had something to back
myself up in front of His Majesty.

20:03.631 --> 20:04.771
Now look what's happened.

20:04.951 --> 20:08.091
His Majesty demoted me to take charge
of the military in South City.

20:08.271 --> 20:10.070
The son is praised
while the father is scorned.

20:10.071 --> 20:11.270
You're putting me down,

20:11.271 --> 20:13.651
and you think Jiang Meisun
did it out of good will?

20:13.671 --> 20:15.171
Father, that's...

20:16.111 --> 20:17.931
Do you still take me as your father?

20:18.471 --> 20:20.910
All this while, you've stationed
yourself in Futing

20:20.911 --> 20:23.091
and hardly ever came home.

20:23.151 --> 20:25.171
His Majesty praised you
in a royal edict,

20:25.511 --> 20:27.811
saying how you take after Jiang Meisun.

20:28.311 --> 20:29.931
What a joke I've become.

20:30.271 --> 20:32.211
Whose son are you really?

20:41.571 --> 20:42.970
Perfume sachets, ornaments...

20:42.971 --> 20:44.160
Candied hawthorns...

20:44.161 --> 20:45.631
Come take a look.

20:46.531 --> 20:48.980
Perfume sachets, ornaments,
little trinkets.

20:48.981 --> 20:51.231
Powder and rouge.

20:51.281 --> 20:52.640
Come and take a look.

20:52.641 --> 20:53.530
Is it there?

20:53.531 --> 20:54.540
- I'll take you.
- Let's get you a little tiger.

20:54.541 --> 20:55.681
Okay.

21:03.431 --> 21:04.571
Do you like it?

21:10.071 --> 21:12.091
Whose son are you really?

21:12.351 --> 21:14.990
His lordship has always been strict

21:14.991 --> 21:16.411
with you since young.

21:16.831 --> 21:20.251
It's true that there are more rules
in the duke's household.

21:24.871 --> 21:26.171
Today, I realized.

21:26.991 --> 21:28.251
After being away for so long,

21:28.511 --> 21:29.771
my parents and little brother

21:30.031 --> 21:32.131
are what a real family is like.

21:32.791 --> 21:34.011
My coming back suddenly

21:34.351 --> 21:36.171
seemed to have disrupted their harmony.

21:40.651 --> 21:41.891
I want to take a stroll alone.

21:42.511 --> 21:43.651
You may leave.

21:53.711 --> 21:55.710
Today, this shadow puppet show

21:55.711 --> 21:57.811
I'm putting on today

21:57.911 --> 22:00.651
is called the Records of the Enlightened Age.

22:01.151 --> 22:03.251
- Nice.
- Awesome!

22:22.111 --> 22:27.731
(Happiness)

22:30.771 --> 22:32.931
- Take a look.
- Ornaments...

22:32.951 --> 22:34.971
(If I weren't the son
of Duke of Ying,)

22:35.831 --> 22:37.811
(would it have been better
for everyone?)

22:41.271 --> 22:45.171
(Suona, sedan, happiness)
Nice!

23:04.991 --> 23:06.790
(Happiness)

23:06.791 --> 23:09.251
- Nice.
- Nice.

23:22.171 --> 23:23.510
It's been so long
since we came to the capital.

23:23.511 --> 23:24.870
The new year celebration here
is much livelier.

23:24.871 --> 23:26.390
There are so many shows and masks.

23:26.391 --> 23:27.950
We're going to be late
if we don't make a move.

23:27.951 --> 23:30.131
Why did you ladies get off here?

23:30.231 --> 23:31.430
Fifth Master and Seventh Master
are waiting.

23:31.431 --> 23:32.430
Come, get in the carriage.

23:32.431 --> 23:33.971
Go on, quickly.

23:46.901 --> 23:47.750
Young ladies,

23:47.751 --> 23:49.511
I will notify Fifth Master
and Seventh Master.

23:51.551 --> 23:52.691
Fourth Young Lady.

23:57.111 --> 24:00.790
Chen Shiyuan, Liu Xuezhen, Pang Kunbai.

24:00.791 --> 24:03.891
The guests are all new nobles
in the court.

24:04.351 --> 24:05.611
Know yourself and your opponent.

24:05.631 --> 24:07.331
Being prepared means less worries.

24:09.751 --> 24:11.411
There are so many male guests.

24:11.671 --> 24:12.630
With so many young guys,

24:12.631 --> 24:14.430
I should've dressed up nicer.

24:14.431 --> 24:16.150
The guests are mainly
Fifth Uncle's students,

24:16.151 --> 24:17.531
members of nobility.

24:18.271 --> 24:19.830
This is after all a banquet of honor.

24:19.831 --> 24:21.971
Our attire is indeed disrespectful.

24:22.471 --> 24:23.611
Sister.

24:26.551 --> 24:27.630
Sister.

24:27.631 --> 24:28.851
How come you're here?

24:32.591 --> 24:34.051
You look dashing, Ming.

24:36.111 --> 24:37.691
I just followed Mother's instructions.

24:37.911 --> 24:39.931
I didn't know you'd be here today.

24:43.631 --> 24:44.891
There are many guests.

24:45.511 --> 24:46.630
Why don't you come to my room

24:46.631 --> 24:48.640
and I'll help you get dressed? Come.

24:48.641 --> 24:49.811
- Zhao.
- No...

24:50.911 --> 24:52.171
You're finally here.

24:52.751 --> 24:54.731
Master and Fifth Brother
are all waiting for you.

24:55.111 --> 24:55.950
Ming,

24:55.951 --> 24:58.051
why didn't you tell us Zhao is here?

24:58.991 --> 25:00.131
Follow me.

25:00.831 --> 25:01.971
It's this way.

25:07.391 --> 25:08.390
Master,

25:08.391 --> 25:09.990
- Zhao and the girls are here.
- Yes.

25:09.991 --> 25:12.411
Not bad, they're young and talented.

25:14.431 --> 25:15.571
Ms. Longevity.

25:17.891 --> 25:19.251
The residence is hosting a banquet

25:19.311 --> 25:21.571
and our guests are notable members
of the society.

25:21.751 --> 25:23.491
How could you show up late

25:24.031 --> 25:25.691
and dressed up like that?

25:25.871 --> 25:27.331
Standing next to Ming,

25:27.591 --> 25:28.790
you look more like a servant.

25:28.791 --> 25:30.891
Ms. Longevity lives
with her grandmother.

25:31.231 --> 25:32.611
It's good to be simple and neat.

25:33.131 --> 25:34.430
It's my fault.

25:34.431 --> 25:37.301
I forgot to tell the ladies
the specifics.

25:37.591 --> 25:38.378
(Pang Kunbai)
Let me take them

25:38.379 --> 25:39.811
(Pang Kunbai)
to get dressed.

25:40.351 --> 25:41.491
Come.

25:43.341 --> 25:44.390
Apologies, Fifth Uncle.

25:44.391 --> 25:46.211
My sisters and I are dressed plainly

25:46.271 --> 25:47.931
not because
we were deliberately neglectful.

25:48.211 --> 25:50.451
It's because dressing too lavishly
is inappropriate.

25:52.111 --> 25:53.470
What do you mean?

25:53.471 --> 25:56.011
Since last year, natural disasters
have been frequently occurring.

25:56.111 --> 25:57.371
On top of that, wars raged on.

25:57.371 --> 25:58.950
In the start of the year,
the Emperor and Empress

25:58.951 --> 26:00.931
took the initiative to cut down
on luxury items.

26:01.071 --> 26:03.691
They called on the officials
to not waste resources.

26:04.111 --> 26:05.510
I heard that Fifth Uncle

26:05.511 --> 26:07.551
is about to be promoted to head of
the Ministry of Rites.

26:07.551 --> 26:09.510
Despite not having received
the official notice,

26:09.511 --> 26:11.011
being so high profile and extravagant

26:11.511 --> 26:13.331
could give others a reason
to make trouble.

26:13.351 --> 26:14.491
Well...

26:15.311 --> 26:16.531
That is true.

26:17.151 --> 26:19.310
It didn't cross my mind at all.

26:19.311 --> 26:20.430
For special celebrations,

26:20.431 --> 26:23.051
even commoners would dress up.

26:23.111 --> 26:24.750
It's for the sake of auspiciousness.

26:24.751 --> 26:25.590
How is this

26:25.591 --> 26:27.430
related to a national affair, Zhou?

26:27.431 --> 26:29.130
It is quite a relief to hear such

26:29.131 --> 26:31.210
down-to-earth words from a lady

26:31.211 --> 26:32.601
from an official family.

26:35.831 --> 26:36.971
Who's that?

26:38.171 --> 26:39.891
Of course it had to be
the Fourth Young Lady.

26:43.791 --> 26:44.790
Mr. Wu.

26:44.791 --> 26:46.091
Long time no see.

26:46.111 --> 26:47.840
Is Mr. Wu Sr. doing well?

26:47.841 --> 26:49.150
Grandfather is as fine as can be.

26:49.151 --> 26:50.496
(Wu Shan, Wu Family's Eldest Grandchild)
I wish Fifth Master Dou congratulations

26:50.497 --> 26:52.391
(Wu Shan, Wu Family's Eldest Grandchild)
on behalf of my grandfather.

26:52.631 --> 26:54.051
- Mr. Dou.
- Thank you.

27:03.391 --> 27:04.990
- Mr. Wu.
- Take down the lights.

27:04.991 --> 27:05.840
Please head inside.

27:05.841 --> 27:07.051
- Madam.
- Head inside.

27:07.191 --> 27:08.691
Help Ming to change her clothes.

27:16.751 --> 27:19.491
Is that Prime Minister Wu's
sole grandchild, Wu Shan?

27:20.151 --> 27:22.811
I didn't know you had dealings
with the Wu family.

27:23.071 --> 27:25.211
My stepmother is the people person.

27:25.831 --> 27:28.531
Moreover, Wang Xingyi
was Wu Shan's examiner.

27:28.751 --> 27:31.531
He's likely the arrow
at this private banquet.

27:32.111 --> 27:33.670
And between Dou Ming and I,

27:33.671 --> 27:35.091
one of us is the bullseye.

27:41.871 --> 27:43.350
They're really changing the lanterns?

27:43.351 --> 27:44.710
(Bright Moon Clear Spring)
You're incredible, Mr. Chen.

27:44.711 --> 27:45.504
(Su Xin, Su Lan)
You even predicted

27:45.505 --> 27:46.510
(Su Xin, Su Lan)
that they would change the lanterns

27:46.511 --> 27:47.630
halfway through the banquet.

27:47.631 --> 27:49.251
Switching out the celebratory lanterns

27:49.751 --> 27:52.771
means Fourth Young Lady
is doing alright.

27:54.231 --> 27:55.971
Perhaps she's even gotten
the upper hand.

27:58.551 --> 27:59.950
Let us go, Mother.

27:59.951 --> 28:01.331
Ming, answer me.

28:01.591 --> 28:02.670
Just now at the door,

28:02.671 --> 28:03.950
what were you doing

28:03.951 --> 28:05.091
with Dou Zhao?

28:06.671 --> 28:09.350
I just had
a little catch-up with sister.

28:09.351 --> 28:11.470
She doesn't see you as her sister.

28:11.471 --> 28:12.771
Don't be a fool.

28:12.871 --> 28:14.731
Stop being so eager
to call her your sister.

28:15.311 --> 28:17.691
Everything I do is for your own good.

28:17.691 --> 28:19.110
Otherwise, why did I
go through the trouble

28:19.111 --> 28:21.011
to invite Mr. Wu here?

28:21.191 --> 28:22.670
But I don't have any...

28:22.671 --> 28:23.811
Shut your mouth.

28:24.471 --> 28:26.030
When choosing a husband,

28:26.031 --> 28:28.451
your own feelings
is the lowest priority.

28:29.651 --> 28:31.901
Mr. Wu is from an established family.

28:32.111 --> 28:33.731
Moreover, he's kind and diligent.

28:33.831 --> 28:36.091
He makes the perfect husband material.

28:38.151 --> 28:39.531
You're of the age to get married.

28:39.671 --> 28:40.971
You're at your prime.

28:41.111 --> 28:42.251
So tonight,

28:42.511 --> 28:44.350
make sure you make me proud.

28:44.351 --> 28:45.491
Got it?

28:46.271 --> 28:47.611
- Yes.
- Let's go.

28:56.231 --> 28:57.371
Ms. Longevity.

29:01.831 --> 29:04.971
It was a slight of hand
mentioning official affairs.

29:05.631 --> 29:06.851
I'm dressed plainly

29:07.191 --> 29:09.291
because Mother's death anniversary
is coming up.

29:10.191 --> 29:12.051
I don't know
if you still remember, Father.

29:13.071 --> 29:14.331
Of course I do.

29:16.791 --> 29:18.131
Look at this magnolia tree.

29:18.591 --> 29:21.171
I'm the one taking care of it.

29:21.751 --> 29:24.211
The blooms
are particularly beautiful this year.

29:25.101 --> 29:26.411
Flowers can bloom again,

29:26.441 --> 29:27.971
but humans cannot start over.

29:29.231 --> 29:32.110
Whether it's the new year
or a promotion, they're just excuses.

29:32.111 --> 29:33.651
Father and Fifth Uncle

29:33.651 --> 29:35.710
are taking this opportunity
to get Prime Minister Wu's grandson

29:35.711 --> 29:36.870
and other guests

29:36.871 --> 29:38.651
to check out the Dous' daughters, right?

29:40.551 --> 29:41.750
Your fifth uncle

29:41.751 --> 29:43.931
is only looking out
for your potential suitor.

29:44.991 --> 29:47.091
Made to look inferior
and scrutinized by others,

29:47.091 --> 29:48.190
did you expect me and Fifth Sister

29:48.191 --> 29:50.291
to spread our tails like peacocks
to please those men?

29:50.391 --> 29:52.431
The seniors only have
your best interests at heart.

29:52.471 --> 29:53.891
Don't take it wrongly.

29:54.071 --> 29:54.990
Fifth Uncle

29:54.991 --> 29:56.891
insisted you take Wang Yingxue
as a concubine

29:56.911 --> 29:58.811
so that he could use
the Wang family as backup.

29:59.151 --> 30:01.230
Now, he's moved from
the governor of internal affairs

30:01.231 --> 30:02.950
to the head of the Ministry of Rites.

30:02.951 --> 30:04.750
Does he really need to use my marriage

30:04.751 --> 30:06.430
to help connect him to the Wu family?

30:06.431 --> 30:07.571
Dou Zhao,

30:07.891 --> 30:09.571
you are being too harsh
toward your senior.

30:10.171 --> 30:12.190
Since before, it's the parent's job
to arrange their children's marriage.

30:12.191 --> 30:13.310
But have I ever
forced anything upon you?

30:13.311 --> 30:14.771
No, you didn't force me,

30:14.791 --> 30:16.171
nor did you ever educate me.

30:16.311 --> 30:17.430
Just stay at arm's length.

30:17.431 --> 30:18.790
It's fine to stay out
of each other's business.

30:18.791 --> 30:20.270
- You...
- It's better for you

30:20.271 --> 30:21.990
to place your hopes and dreams
onto Fifth Sister.

30:21.991 --> 30:23.171
When she finds a suitor,

30:23.271 --> 30:24.791
I will be happy to prepare her dowry.

30:32.431 --> 30:34.110
Fifth Young Lady looks weak
like a willow.

30:34.111 --> 30:35.371
She seems a little pitiful.

30:35.671 --> 30:37.371
I reckon she'd be hard to please.

30:37.431 --> 30:40.331
Fifth Young Lady is meant for Mr. Wu.

30:40.431 --> 30:41.510
You can forget about her.

30:41.511 --> 30:43.491
If you want to get
a foot into the Dou family,

30:43.831 --> 30:46.611
you'll have to pick someone
from the unwanted pile,

30:46.671 --> 30:47.851
the last in line.

30:47.951 --> 30:49.211
For instance, the Zhao.

30:49.431 --> 30:50.971
I rather go for Fourth Young Lady then.

30:51.191 --> 30:52.470
At least she's loaded.

30:52.471 --> 30:54.350
Fourth Young Lady is my pick.

30:54.351 --> 30:55.971
You can have Miss Miao.

30:56.111 --> 30:58.171
Although her family background
is lacking,

30:58.231 --> 31:00.451
at least she's moldable.

31:00.671 --> 31:02.750
A gentleman should think twice
before doing anything.

31:02.751 --> 31:04.590
How could you discuss such vile ideas

31:04.591 --> 31:05.950
under the eaves of the Dou residence?

31:05.951 --> 31:07.571
What happened
to the lessons you learned

31:07.631 --> 31:09.131
about the ways of the saint?

31:17.351 --> 31:18.310
Just listen to me.

31:18.311 --> 31:20.270
Pick Miss Miao and you're set.

31:20.271 --> 31:21.411
Listen to me.

31:26.831 --> 31:28.171
What's this?

31:28.551 --> 31:29.931
It smells nasty!

31:35.271 --> 31:37.520
This is a special rain gauge
made by the Ministry of Works.

31:37.521 --> 31:39.711
It's used by counties and cities to
measure rainfall and prevent disasters.

31:39.711 --> 31:40.851
You can't simply touch it.

31:50.671 --> 31:51.931
Ming is here.

31:57.871 --> 31:59.470
The main protagonist is here.

31:59.471 --> 32:01.150
So we just have to be
the supporting cast?

32:01.151 --> 32:01.990
Yes.

32:01.991 --> 32:03.190
Act dumb and guileless.

32:03.191 --> 32:04.811
Focus on eating and drinking.

32:05.031 --> 32:06.771
Okay, I can do that.

32:07.311 --> 32:09.630
Everyone, we are fortunate
to be gathered here.

32:09.631 --> 32:10.670
Please don't be shy.

32:10.671 --> 32:11.971
- Here.
- Sister.

32:17.911 --> 32:19.771
Since you are all well-educated,

32:20.031 --> 32:21.171
I have a suggestion.

32:21.431 --> 32:22.571
Please come up with a couplet

32:22.871 --> 32:24.691
and invite one of the ladies
to match it.

32:24.751 --> 32:27.331
If by chance, someone makes
a good follow-up,

32:27.351 --> 32:28.750
- they'll get one drink.
- Good idea.

32:28.751 --> 32:29.590
Good idea.

32:29.591 --> 32:31.131
That's a good idea.

32:32.031 --> 32:33.510
Since Lord Dou has spoken,

32:33.511 --> 32:35.430
it is an honor to be able to see
the literary talent

32:35.431 --> 32:36.611
of the ladies.

32:36.631 --> 32:40.051
Alright, then.
Let's have Mr. Wu go first.

32:47.951 --> 32:49.611
A lane by the walls shaded with willows,

32:49.612 --> 32:50.950
floodwaters submerge
the long embankment.

32:50.951 --> 32:53.251
There's no ground left to tread
where cattle and sheep plod.

32:53.911 --> 32:55.091
Good one.

32:55.431 --> 32:58.411
Dezhen's literary talent
is not inferior to Hanlin's.

33:24.791 --> 33:25.931
Ming.

33:29.031 --> 33:30.211
Write this.

33:39.071 --> 33:40.851
(A different world opens up
under the heavens)

33:42.071 --> 33:43.531
Dou Ming has a follow-up.

33:44.511 --> 33:46.611
Beyond the heart lies Shangri-la,

33:46.611 --> 33:48.070
clouds obscure the narrow path ahead.

33:48.071 --> 33:49.891
Through the woods
where chickens and dogs are heard,

33:49.892 --> 33:51.611
a different world opens up
under the heavens.

33:51.631 --> 33:52.851
Excellent.

33:53.111 --> 33:55.091
It's the perfect pairing.

34:01.431 --> 34:03.011
Thanks to Mr. Wu for the inspiration.

34:08.111 --> 34:09.971
Shishu, take a look at this verse.

34:12.551 --> 34:13.691
Here.

34:26.111 --> 34:27.910
Fifth Young Lady
is totally in the spotlight.

34:27.911 --> 34:29.870
Wang Yingxue must be delighted.

34:29.871 --> 34:31.910
Hasn't this rhyming gone long enough?

34:31.911 --> 34:32.780
Yeah, Ms. Longevity.

34:32.781 --> 34:35.411
That's how she's always been.

34:35.631 --> 34:37.250
Fourth Young Lady is intelligent.

34:37.251 --> 34:39.171
How come you've not produced any verse?

34:39.911 --> 34:41.390
I grew up in the countryside,

34:41.391 --> 34:42.531
so I'm not good in writing.

34:43.391 --> 34:44.731
You jest, miss.

34:44.871 --> 34:47.251
The young ladies are the stars
of today's banquet.

34:47.711 --> 34:50.011
How about the Fourth Young Lady
set a verse this time?

34:56.231 --> 34:57.110
Ms. Longevity,

34:57.111 --> 34:58.731
do you not want to write?

34:58.751 --> 35:00.371
I can do it for you.

35:19.501 --> 35:23.211
A young child from the north
tends the herds,

35:23.311 --> 35:26.971
watching over sheep, cattle,
and the stars.

35:29.391 --> 35:30.571
I can match it.

35:31.551 --> 35:34.931
The old rogue in black
launches a midnight ambush,

35:35.231 --> 35:38.851
seeking to hold, to embrace,
and to steal a kiss.

35:47.431 --> 35:48.611
How shameless.

35:54.311 --> 35:55.430
Ridiculous.

35:55.431 --> 35:56.731
From the handwriting,

35:57.071 --> 35:59.171
it looks like Miss Zhao wrote it.

35:59.591 --> 36:02.491
Zhao Si is a two-time participant of
the Ministry of Rites exam nonetheless.

36:02.671 --> 36:04.011
You are his only daughter.

36:04.551 --> 36:06.571
How could you be so crass and absurd?

36:07.431 --> 36:09.451
You did a good job
following up though, Mr. Pang.

36:09.711 --> 36:11.691
What about I pull
the red thread for you?

36:12.031 --> 36:14.731
You could be the Zhaos'
matrilocal son-in-law.

36:14.791 --> 36:16.611
I never said I wanted him.

36:16.791 --> 36:18.851
Apologies for my rudeness.

36:19.871 --> 36:21.550
He thought Zhao had written it,

36:21.551 --> 36:22.830
that's why he tried comic relief.

36:22.831 --> 36:24.430
It was only a joke.

36:24.431 --> 36:26.451
When the tree is rotten,

36:26.551 --> 36:28.251
you can't expect the fruit
to be any good.

36:28.471 --> 36:30.211
Miss Zhao's parents are away in Diannan.

36:30.431 --> 36:31.870
She lacks proper upbringing.

36:31.871 --> 36:34.491
After spending years in the countryside
with merchants,

36:34.551 --> 36:36.571
it's inevitable
she'd be unknowledgeable.

36:36.591 --> 36:38.251
Stop your crap!

36:41.511 --> 36:42.651
There, there.

36:42.911 --> 36:44.251
If you're right,

36:44.591 --> 36:46.251
I too, grew up without my parents.

36:46.311 --> 36:48.511
So I'm doing menial jobs
and wandering in the countryside.

36:48.511 --> 36:49.651
Dou Zhao.

36:53.631 --> 36:54.771
Perfect.

36:54.911 --> 36:56.331
I just thought of a first verse.

36:57.911 --> 36:59.051
Ms. Longevity.

37:00.071 --> 37:02.190
What? What's she doing on this side?

37:02.191 --> 37:03.910
Dou Zhao, that's the men's area.

37:03.911 --> 37:05.070
How could you cross over?

37:05.071 --> 37:05.910
Aren't you ashamed?

37:05.911 --> 37:07.051
Dou Zhao...

37:11.371 --> 37:13.070
The gentlemen were discussing
the ladies' marriages

37:13.071 --> 37:14.571
without a care in the world.

37:14.751 --> 37:15.971
If they aren't ashamed,

37:16.031 --> 37:17.171
why should I?

37:21.271 --> 37:22.910
The fan is only used by courtesans

37:22.911 --> 37:24.371
or talented scholars.

37:25.191 --> 37:26.670
Mr. Liu Xuezhen.

37:26.671 --> 37:27.830
I heard you sat
for the imperial exam six times

37:27.831 --> 37:28.870
and failed six times.

37:28.871 --> 37:30.350
You're using the fan,

37:30.351 --> 37:32.291
so what talent do you have to show?

37:34.311 --> 37:35.891
You're a lady, miss.

37:36.111 --> 37:37.331
Your words

37:37.431 --> 37:38.430
are inappropriate.

37:38.431 --> 37:39.910
Mr. Chen Shiyuan.

37:39.911 --> 37:41.390
I heard your family business went bust

37:41.391 --> 37:42.910
and you even had to sell
your ancestral home.

37:42.911 --> 37:45.251
I bet you're hoping to use the dowry
to plug the holes.

37:46.331 --> 37:48.110
Ms. Longevity has been away
from the capital.

37:48.111 --> 37:49.451
How did she know...

37:50.391 --> 37:51.891
(Price treasure)

37:56.631 --> 37:58.411
A fickle lover is easy to find,

37:58.791 --> 38:00.331
but a priceless treasure
is hard to seek.

38:01.111 --> 38:05.091
Why entrust insincere feelings
to embellished letters?

38:05.431 --> 38:07.910
I can't stand you talentless
and immoral people

38:07.911 --> 38:09.331
who curry favor with the powerful.

38:09.331 --> 38:11.790
Just because you know a few characters,
you think you're superior,

38:11.791 --> 38:13.251
talking ill of the ladies.

38:13.271 --> 38:15.630
You treat marriage
like an item on the shelf,

38:15.631 --> 38:17.131
comparing and commenting on it.

38:18.271 --> 38:20.611
You deem us the unwanted bunch,
last in the line.

38:20.831 --> 38:22.390
Does that make you the despicable fly?

38:22.391 --> 38:23.531
Don't be rude.

38:23.911 --> 38:25.331
You're behaving inappropriately

38:25.431 --> 38:27.411
and making wild remarks
in front of guests.

38:27.451 --> 38:28.430
Where are your manners?

38:28.431 --> 38:29.731
That's Zhao for you.

38:30.591 --> 38:32.630
Mr. Wu, sorry you had to see that.

38:32.631 --> 38:34.051
Fourth Young Lady Dou's couplet

38:34.231 --> 38:35.491
is sincere and straightforward.

38:35.711 --> 38:37.611
There's a bit of sarcastic humor too.

38:38.231 --> 38:39.491
I actually think

38:39.951 --> 38:41.291
there's nothing wrong with it.

38:41.791 --> 38:44.971
But, it does make it harder
to create the other couplet.

38:46.071 --> 38:47.451
I am too crass and unrefined.

38:48.071 --> 38:49.731
I am not qualified
to be among such company.

38:50.251 --> 38:51.651
Allow me to leave and self-reflect.

38:57.151 --> 38:58.451
- Me too.
- Me too.

38:59.151 --> 39:00.451
Let them be.

39:05.911 --> 39:07.531
Will Fourth Young Lady be okay?

39:09.871 --> 39:13.531
A noble family
knows to assess the situation.

39:14.271 --> 39:17.731
Being too aggressive
may not be a good thing.

39:18.711 --> 39:23.131
It will depend on whether
Fourth Young Lady can hold it in.

39:23.871 --> 39:25.291
If she can,

39:26.151 --> 39:28.411
we'll have to wait
for another 15 minutes.

39:28.631 --> 39:31.051
You're always so cryptic, Mr. Chen.

39:32.131 --> 39:33.821
What happens if she can't hold it in?

39:34.431 --> 39:35.691
Wait up, Zhao!

39:36.551 --> 39:37.630
She's here.

39:37.631 --> 39:40.150
Don't be angry, Zhao.

39:40.151 --> 39:41.411
I'm not.

39:41.791 --> 39:43.811
I can't be bothered with those people.

39:46.151 --> 39:48.950
Are you sure you're not angry, miss?

39:48.951 --> 39:50.651
I am a little upset.

39:51.351 --> 39:53.510
So you asked me to attend the banquet

39:53.511 --> 39:55.331
hoping I'd keep a low profile.

39:57.911 --> 39:59.651
But it's not all bad.

40:00.101 --> 40:01.910
When choosing a wife,

40:01.911 --> 40:04.131
officials value virtue
and respect the most.

40:04.551 --> 40:05.910
Now that I'm seen

40:05.911 --> 40:07.691
as the wild, fierce girl,

40:07.851 --> 40:10.901
it will be the perfect excuse to reject
Marquis of Jining's marriage proposal.

40:10.911 --> 40:12.931
Now they can't force me to get married.

40:13.071 --> 40:15.270
Do you really not care about
your reputation

40:15.271 --> 40:16.491
and marriage at all?

40:16.631 --> 40:17.830
Women can live a good life

40:17.831 --> 40:19.451
even without men.

40:20.071 --> 40:23.051
When you become the wife,
you have to look after both families.

40:23.511 --> 40:26.171
Worrying about his career,
taking care of household chores,

40:26.751 --> 40:29.011
not to mention the concubines
and illegitimate children.

40:29.431 --> 40:30.931
If your feelings were true,

40:31.831 --> 40:33.691
you'd likely end up like my mother.

40:37.391 --> 40:39.670
Still, I want to meet my one true love,

40:39.671 --> 40:41.091
get married and have children.

40:41.431 --> 40:44.411
Maybe it's because
I grew up without my parents,

40:44.471 --> 40:46.611
so I've always wanted a family.

40:46.751 --> 40:48.131
If you think...

40:51.231 --> 40:53.691
I'm going to teach
those uneducated slimes a lesson!

40:53.791 --> 40:55.830
How dare they say I'm too old,
crass and unfavorable?

40:55.831 --> 40:57.430
- I'll show them what's up.
- Zhangru...

40:57.431 --> 40:59.510
I, Zhao Zhangru, will show you
what it means to be crass!

40:59.511 --> 41:01.150
Zhangru, get back here.

41:01.151 --> 41:02.030
Sit down.

41:02.031 --> 41:03.211
Zhangru.

41:03.711 --> 41:06.390
Those people are blind and heartless.

41:06.391 --> 41:08.211
They couldn't see your greatness.

41:10.531 --> 41:11.390
That's right.

41:11.391 --> 41:13.510
If my father hadn't insisted
on finding a matrilocal son-in-law,

41:13.511 --> 41:15.611
I would've gotten married long ago.

41:17.471 --> 41:18.910
Okay, okay, she's drunk.

41:18.911 --> 41:20.611
I'll take her back first.

41:20.871 --> 41:22.011
Come on.

41:22.271 --> 41:23.110
I'm bored.

41:23.111 --> 41:24.510
I'll go for a walk outside.

41:24.511 --> 41:26.451
Okay. Don't stay out too late.

41:26.951 --> 41:28.091
Let's go, this way.

41:28.351 --> 41:30.270
Su, drink with me some more.

41:30.271 --> 41:31.411
Okay, we'll drink.

41:51.471 --> 41:52.611
Miss,

41:52.671 --> 41:53.891
there's someone following us.

41:54.711 --> 41:56.211
Miss, have a look.

41:59.272 --> 42:00.310
Go back to Dou's Residence

42:00.311 --> 42:01.591
and bring me some silver notes.

42:01.671 --> 42:03.371
Will do, miss.

42:11.311 --> 42:12.451
See you around.

42:18.911 --> 42:21.870
(Show, Story of Luo Shan)

42:21.871 --> 42:22.870
Sir.

42:22.871 --> 42:24.371
The newly released Story of Luo Shan.

42:24.591 --> 42:26.851
The son who lost his mother early
takes his father to court

42:26.911 --> 42:29.270
A life of wandering,
heartache and grievances.

42:29.271 --> 42:30.931
You can't cut off your father for good.

42:31.571 --> 42:33.030
There are still some seats available.

42:33.031 --> 42:34.251
Why don't you head in?

42:35.871 --> 42:37.110
Drinks and snacks are provided.

42:37.111 --> 42:38.291
It's the whole package.

42:41.231 --> 42:45.251
(Show, Story of Luo Shan)

42:47.871 --> 42:49.011
Welcome.

43:13.071 --> 43:15.310
I invited Ji Jianming
to countryside manor

43:15.311 --> 43:17.790
hoping he and Ms. Longevity
would take a liking to each other.

43:17.791 --> 43:19.630
That Ji and Ms. Longevity
keep meeting up in private.

43:19.631 --> 43:20.851
He must have feelings for her.

43:21.111 --> 43:22.190
Zhao,

43:22.191 --> 43:23.630
how far have you two progressed?

43:23.631 --> 43:24.771
Watch out!

43:28.931 --> 43:31.601
♪The golden fiery steed
rides across the vast horizon♪

43:32.041 --> 43:35.290
♪In this life, oh♪

43:35.291 --> 43:36.970
♪Without you♪

43:36.971 --> 43:40.591
♪What is there to envy?♪

43:41.051 --> 43:43.530
♪Let me lay down my blade
and leave the sea of battles♪

43:43.531 --> 43:47.850
♪To adorn your hair with a jade hairpin♪

43:47.851 --> 43:50.040
♪Let a thousand, ten thousand blossoms♪

43:50.041 --> 43:54.491
♪Bloom in a single night for you♪

43:54.641 --> 43:57.770
♪The splendor of the world
is but fleeting sorrow♪

43:57.771 --> 44:00.861
♪Should the flames of war arise♪

44:01.201 --> 44:04.450
♪I shall hold your hand♪

44:04.451 --> 44:07.430
♪And walk through the dust♪

44:07.431 --> 44:09.640
♪I want to hold you in my arms♪

44:09.641 --> 44:13.930
♪Leaving the world behind♪

44:13.931 --> 44:16.240
♪From now on,
all the vast wonders of the world♪

44:16.241 --> 44:20.490
♪May be left as blank spaces♪

44:20.491 --> 44:24.191
♪The dazzling spring moon over the city♪

44:24.371 --> 44:27.431
♪Is no match for your beauty♪

44:27.601 --> 44:32.811
♪Why ascend to high towers again?♪

44:33.611 --> 44:35.870
♪I will lay down my blade
and leave the sea of battles♪

44:35.871 --> 44:37.510
♪Break my spear to crown you♪

44:37.511 --> 44:40.230
♪With a golden-branch hairpin♪

44:40.231 --> 44:42.350
♪Let a thousand, ten thousand blossoms♪

44:42.351 --> 44:46.460
♪Bloom for you♪

44:46.461 --> 44:50.221
♪No more guarding lonely towers♪

44:50.261 --> 44:53.580
♪Spring is near, ripe for the taking♪

44:53.581 --> 44:54.920
♪Holding your hand♪

44:54.921 --> 44:59.871
♪Till we reach beyond the noise♪

45:00.311 --> 45:03.461
♪Only for you, I shall paint♪

45:03.651 --> 45:06.441
♪With bold strokes and vibrant colors♪

45:06.631 --> 45:08.480
♪And for all else♪

45:08.481 --> 45:15.471
♪Let it remain pale and void♪

45:18.311 --> 45:19.230
(No animals were harmed
in the making of this drama)

45:19.231 --> 45:20.190
(Every medical behaviour involved
and medicine used in the drama)

45:20.191 --> 45:21.531
(is required by the story.
Please don't try this at home)
